<plot>In order to marry his sweetheart Marion Shilling, prizefighter Lloyd Hughes accepts a fight against her brother George Lewis. Unknown to him, the brother has a condition that renders him unfit to be in a boxing ring. The brother is killed when the fighter hits him with a punch to the heart and the fighter vows to fight no more. But circumstances forces him back to the ring.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?563873</url></doc>
